Package: tcp-gateway
Version: 0.4.1
Section: net
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: Hans Bengtsson
Depends: systemd, python3, python3-venv, python3-pip, iputils-ping
Description: TCP Gateway Connectivity Validation Service
 Secure REST API based connectivity validation gateway.
 Supports TCP, HTTP/HTTPS and ICMP connectivity checks.
 Provides automation integration through authenticated API access.
